Package pt.ipp.isep.dei.esoft.project.domain

Class Entry

java.lang.Object
pt.ipp.isep.dei.esoft.project.domain.Entry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Entry extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an entry in a project schedule. An entry consists of a task, urgency, duration, associated green space, status, start and end dates, team assigned, and vehicles assigned.
